creator: BinaryApps Studio
descriptionHtml:
PDF Printer is a perfect smart phone application used to print pdf files using smart phone device. PDF Printer allows you to print PDF files directly from your smart phones. All you need is a printer that supports wifi/bluetooth. Just connect your smart phone with the printer and send a printing command to start printing pdf files from your smart phone.

This PDF printing app, is very smart and efficient printing app which prints pdf files on a single click. Open a desired PDF file adjust your printer setting and tap on print button to start printing you pdf file. Pdf files will start to print in seconds.

Features:

Following are some great features of smart PDF Printer App:

- Print multiple files at once.
- Easily 7 Quick pdf printing app.
- PDF file sharing is added as well.
- Easy to adjust printer settings.
- Set page size and page shape to print accordingly,
- Print important documents like Id cards, driving license.

How to use PDF Printer App:

PDF printer app can be used in three simple steps:

- Open pdf printer app, select your desired PDF file.
- Adjust printer setting by connecting it via wifi.
- Hit “Print” button to start printing.
